QuestData.Title: Admiral Taylor has Awakened
QuestData.Description: It would seem that your Admiral Taylor has awakened from his injuries. He and his people are upstairs.$B$BHe has requested your presence.
QuestData.LogDescription: Speak with Admiral Taylor at Binan Village in Kun-Lai Summit.
QuestData.RewardText: $n, is that you? I can't believe we survived the destruction of the Jade Serpent.$B$BSome of us anyway.
